<h2>So you want to Remote Pair Program?</h2>
<div>First you'll need to find someone to pair with, for which we recommend the <a href="https://plus.google.com/communities/100279740984094902927">G+ Pairing Community</a></div>

<div><br>
</div>

<div>Then you'll need some tools. &nbsp;From most simple to most complex here are a few</div>

<div>
